<Group labelreference="L22" drawlabel="true">
<Input>
<Text-field style="Text" size="16" layout="Normal"><Font size="16">Since the flow is potential the vorticity and divergence are zero.  However the elements of the rate of strain matrix are somewhat complicated and so I use contour plots to look at them.</Font></Text-field>
</Input>
